    @{fg fill}MrMazinga@{fg text} template and tooltypes are:

    - GF=GIFFILE
      The GIFAnim to play.
      Default: Mazinga.gif

    - STRINGS/K
      A file to read strings from. The strings are not empty
      lines, max 512 chars long. Lines beginning with # are
      ignored.
      Default: none defined

    - SCALE/K/N
      10<=SCALE<=400 scale factor
      Not all values are OK, if so the windows is not opened.
      Default: 100

    - TF=TIMEFACTOR/K/N
      An integral number, defining a time factor for the animation
      if <0 anim runs slower, if >0 it runs faster
      Default: 1

    - BD=BACKDROP/S
      Windows is a backdrop one.
      Default: NO.

